description: This is a great match up between two returning veterans. The Amazon has size and experience on her side. The Gymnast is strong, ripped, and flexible. Both hate losing, but only one can emerge the victor. It was a hard fought match and both wrestlers gave it their all. Once again, experience and size won out. The Amazon dominated the Gymnast in a RD 4 I’m sure she will not forget.
title: The Amazon (3-5)
